('Riffusion', 'riffusion', 'Transform lyrics into complete songs with AI-driven music composition.', 'Riffusion is an AI-powered tool that is breaking new ground in the realm of music generation. With a focus on transforming text into song, Riffusion offers a unique platform where users can input lyrics and receive a fully composed song in return. This innovative approach to music creation is designed for musicians, producers, content creators, and anyone interested in exploring the intersection of artificial intelligence and art.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2025-02-14T22-25-28.679Z-6R1HMCysDnN8FeSlH-KrYd6Ia2Xb-I9fD.png', 'https://www.riffusion.com/', 'free', '[{"plan": "Free Access", "price": "Free", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Text-to-Music Conversion","AI-Driven Composition","User-Friendly Interface","Online Sharing Capability"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
('Pi', 'pi', 'AI-powered conversational assistant offering personalized, context-aware interactions.', 'Pi is an innovative AI tool designed to act as a conversational assistant, offering users a personalized and interactive experience. This tool is crafted for individuals and professionals seeking an AI companion that provides thoughtful, context-aware responses across a variety of topics. With its user-centric design, Pi simplifies the process of obtaining information and engaging in meaningful conversations, making it a versatile tool for both personal and professional use.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2025-01-27T21-54-34.209Z-FjI2-ct9K4YCxDYlmqHRuR8ksE4EawnO6.PNG', 'https://heypi.com/talk', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Contextual Conversations","Personalization","Multi-Platform Accessibility","Continuous Learning","Engaging Interactions","Versatility"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
