('VMEG', 'vmeg', 'Localizes videos with AI translation and dubbing.', 'VMEG is an AI-powered video localization platform that transforms how we communicate across languages. Designed to break down language barriers, VMEG offers a suite of tools for video translation, dubbing, and voice cloning, making content accessible to a global audience. Whether you’re a content creator or a multinational corporation, VMEG simplifies the complex task of video localization with ease and precision.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2025-05-09T16-35-24.259Z-ix6kh0sHYbIaApNFC2As1pRPKPwqxKWrX.png', 'https://vmeg.ai/?rc=IltYpNBV', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free", "price": "$0.", "features": []}, {"plan": "Studio", "price": "$20 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Enterprise", "price": "Custom", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"AI Video Translator","AI Subtitle Generator and Translator","Realistic AI Voice Cloning Technology","Lip Sync AI Video Maker","Time Efficiency","Cost-Effective"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
