('Docus', 'docus', 'AI-driven health platform for personalized insights and expert advice.', 'Docus is a cutting-edge AI-powered health platform designed to revolutionize personal health management. By offering a suite of tools such as the AI Doctor, lab test interpretations, and access to top US and European doctors, Docus empowers individuals to make informed health decisions. Tailored for those seeking proactive healthcare solutions, Docus simplifies the complexities of health management through personalized insights and expert advice.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/6eb2bfd2495c6311adc7226bdd772899d4b62e95-2532x1259.jpg', 'https://docus.ai/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Personal AI Doctor","Lab Test Interpretation","Top Doctors Access","Proactive Preventive Care","Data Security","Comprehensive Insights"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
('Juno Research', 'juno-research', 'Instantly gather and analyze human insights with real-time feedback.', 'Juno Research is an advanced AI research platform designed to revolutionize how businesses collect and analyze human insights. It facilitates direct interactions with real people to capture their thoughts, feelings, and experiences, providing quick and actionable data. Juno Research merges the depth of qualitative research with the speed of quantitative methods, offering a robust solution for businesses seeking reliable and rapid insights.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/ee4b42a5c3095d654689b9f47bfc085732ea58c6-1920x1080.png', 'https://heyjuno.co/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Trial", "price": "Free", "features": []}, {"plan": "Subscription Plans", "price": "Custom", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Real-Time Insights","Scalable Interactions","User-Friendly Platform","Cost-Effective Research"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
