('Lumiere 3D', 'lumiere-3d', 'Generate immersive 3D videos for e-commerce and marketing effortlessly.', 'Lumiere is an innovative platform designed to revolutionize the creation of cinematic 3D product videos, tailor-made for social media platforms like Reels, Shorts, and TikTok. It streamlines the video production process, allowing users to generate high-quality 3D animations of products without the need for complex software or extensive technical skills. By focusing on ease of use and browser-based accessibility, Lumiere empowers individuals and professionals to turn marketing ideas into engaging visual narratives.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/0732079080fdf4b0dae38d14d98898e7638d233f-2506x1257.jpg', 'https://www.lumiere3d.ai/', 'paid', '[{"plan": "DemoFree Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}, {"plan": "Early Access", "price": "$29", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"AI Operator","Smart Scanner","3D Scenes","Easy-to-Use Interface","No Downloads Required","Time-Efficient"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
