('MyEssayWriter.ai', 'myessaywriter-ai', 'Streamlines essay writing with AI, ensuring originality and quality.', 'In the vast sea of AI-driven academic tools, MyEssayWriter.ai emerges as a formidable ally for students, educators, and professionals alike, aiming to streamline the essay writing process. At its core, MyEssayWriter.ai is designed to alleviate the stress associated with writing and structuring essays. By leveraging advanced AI technologies, this tool assists users in generating high-quality, plagiarism-free essays that adhere to academic standards, making it an indispensable resource for anyone looking to enhance their writing efficiency and quality.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/b844c32b9d76d64e49695bf5a26249a3fb0fb976-1640x924.png', 'https://www.myessaywriter.ai/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}, {"plan": "Basic Tier", "price": "$9.99 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Pro Tier", "price": "$14.99 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Advanced Tier", "price": "$99.99 per month", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Paraphrasing Tool","AI Humanizer","AI Detector","Summarizer Tool","Time Efficiency","Enhanced Quality Assurance"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
